   * \underline{S} =
   * J\,\underline{U}^{-1}\,.\,\underline{\sigma}\,.\,\underline{U}^{-1}
   * \f]
   * \param[in] s: corotationnal cauchy stress
   * \param[in] U: stretch tensor
   * \return the second Piola-Kirchhoff stress
